Module FYPMSv2
Package models

Class Request

java.lang.Object
models.Request
Direct Known Subclasses:
ChangeTitleRequest, DeregisterFYPRequest, RegisterFYPRequest, TransferStudentRequest
public abstract class Request extends Object
This class implements a request that is send out be a requestee and received by a responder. This request can than be process by the responder and will make changes when it is processed.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Dennis Chen

      requestID - the request id of the request
      requesterName - the requester's username of the request

    • printRequestDetails

      public abstract void printRequestDetails()
      This method will print all relevant details of this project. The method here is an abstract method because different request type will print different details.

    • processRequest

      public abstract void processRequest()
      This method is the one that will process the request. The method here is an abstract method because different request type will have different processes.
